item.title: CVE-2023-25003|2023-06-23T00:00:00 -- n%2Fa -- autocad%2C%20maya
item.description: A maliciously crafted pskernel.dll file in Autodesk AutoCAD 2023 and Maya 2022 may be used to trigger out-of-bound read write / read vulnerabilities. Exploitation of this vulnerability may lead to code execution.
